    {
      "chinese": "當地有很多可以觀賞的地方，如曲冰遺址、日本鐵管橋、大峽谷在曲冰；摩摩納爾瀑布、武界水壩、一線天、吊橋在武界；過坑有滿坑滿谷的螢火蟲；還有久美的萬興觀及千歲橋。",
      "ab": "Mantan madia’ sala ca na maqtu’ kavila’an, maupas maibuhav is takiqabasan tu bunun, sintas’in is Qai’ial tudiip a tunqaulas danum, mantan manau’az a hunghung iha’an Ququaz acang dii. Maiza ca tupa’un tu Mumunal a tastas, ning’av ha’an Pita’ dii, hunghung is Vaqlac, ciin haundul ha’an acang is Buqaiz dii. \r\n[===]\r\nMaca acang Qatu’ dii ha mantan madia’ sala ca tapucquan. Maca ha’an Namakavan acang dii ha, maizang amin ca sinpasnava’ is sipulas tauluu qabas a qalipucung ciin maqtu’ kavila’an tu haundul.",
      "order": "2",
